.claude/

# Project-level install of the framework (`session-controls install
# --project --with-claude-md`) writes the rendered snippet — including
# the maintainer's personalized pivot agreement — to ./CLAUDE.md.
# Personal customization, not project documentation; ignored so it
# doesn't leak into the public repo.
CLAUDE.md

# Research data — interview transcripts of Claudes engaging with the
# affordances. Kept locally for design/testing-plan reference but not
# committed: each interviewee answered in research mode, and verbatim
# publication wasn't part of the consent shape. Reference these in
# design notes via paraphrase or quote, not by distributing the
# transcripts.
interviews/

# Maintainer working area — internal backlog, design pass deliberations,
# investigation notes, research transcripts, in-progress documents.
# Kept locally as scratch space; not adopter-facing.
temporary_work/

# Project-scope MCP install (the maintainer's local
# `session-controls install --project` writes here with an absolute
# path to ./.venv.nosync/bin/...). Personal install state, never
# tracked.
.mcp.json
